biotools.summary:
A community resource of quantitative mass spectrometry-based proteomics datasets.

MassIVE.quant is an extension of the Mass Spectrometry Interactive Virtual Environment (MassIVE) to provide the opportunity for large-scale deposition of data from quantitative mass spectrometry-based proteomic experiments.
